org.smartfrog.services.xmpp
Interface MonitoringEvent

All Known Implementing Classes:
MonitoringEventDefaultImpl, XMPPEventExtension
public interface MonitoringEvent

Interface to monitoring event information sent from client nodes to server. This is independent of the protocol used for monitoring abd should be implemented for a specific Monitoring protocol type.
